videos.description: Trojans guard Derryck Thornton drives to the hoop and dumps off a pass to Nick Rakocevic for the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: USC's no-look dish leads to and-1

videos.description: Arizona State guard Tra Holder goes to the hoop and finishes with the contested scoop layup.
videos.headline: Sun Devils' Holder finishes acrobatic layup

videos.description: USC's Jordan McLaughlin threads the needle on the break to Nick Rakocevic who converts the contested layup.
videos.headline: USC's great pass leads to tough finish on fast break

videos.description: Trojans' guard Jordan McLaughlin throws the lob pass to Chimezie Metu for the 69-65 lead.
videos.headline: USC's alley-oop dunk extends slim lead

videos.description: Arizona State guard Tra Holder breaks down the game-winning shot he hit against USC, their NCAA Tournament hopes, and the upcoming game against UCLA.
videos.headline: ASU's Holder: 'Told coach I had his back'
